{"tid":1826600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係未應該搞翻地區性遊行呢？","createTime":"2020-01-16T09:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T13:16:05.000Z","uid":332101,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"07921935e20eb90e2e3ed573258d23505f310afd","tid":1826600,"uid":332101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一次開po <br />\n<br />\n見身邊好多人開始變翻港豬<br />\n有d認識嘅手足冇哂目標同方向<br />\n大家好似心灰<br />\n但係我有識嘅手足日日都去貼文宣<br />\n只不過大家都好似要再聚返團火<br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得梁義士同其他唔再係度嘅手足<br />\n七千幾個義士被人拉左<br />\n我真係唔希望場運動就咁不了了之<br />\n我明白呢場係長期抗爭<br />\n但係開始靜落黎都係事實<br />\n<br />\n所以我地其實咪應該搞翻地區性遊行？<br />\n街坊又可以落黎行下<br />\n每個星期日變左抗爭日<br />\n唔一定要衝，打陣地<br />\n好似8月紅土個次咁，行完就走<br />\n每個星期日唔同地方<br />\n又可以keep住團火，又可以當文宣<br />\n又可以幫襯各地區嘅黃店<br />\n<br />\n我明白依家行岀黎都有好大風險<br />\n班狗見人用兩隻腳行路就拉得<br />\n所以大家都要有心理準備<br />\n<br />\n但係最緊要係話俾政府聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場運動未撚完</span></span>"},{"pid":"273e99cb9692f5098d6d88d8370a107f9df93af5","tid":1826600,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"場運動未完, 食黃店當做野, 但食埋藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.19出嚟鞭我屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AJUqon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AJUqon.jpg&h=77332e2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4f19c62693adf727e3232ab1b25069f5f02809c","tid":1826600,"uid":332101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" cl